824
00:41:45,780 --> 00:41:46,850
Coward!

825
00:41:46,850 --> 00:41:48,580
Does it work for you to hide?

826
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:49,980
Well.

827
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:51,610
