829
00:41:53,060 --> 00:41:54,370
Otherwise, that means something happened to you.

830
00:41:54,370 --> 00:41:55,500
I will rush up immediately.

831
00:41:55,500 --> 00:41:57,450
I  reckon when your father is going to take out a stick,

832
00:41:57,450 --> 00:41:59,290
