833
00:42:05,820 --> 00:42:07,410
Don't look at me. That's all I can do.

834
00:42:07,850 --> 00:42:09,340
Then you need to get the timing right.

835
00:42:10,340 --> 00:42:11,500
Go. Go. Go.

836
00:42:39,210 --> 00:42:40,780
Dad. Mom.

837
00:42:41,130 --> 00:42:42,100
You're still awake.

838
00:42:44,020 --> 00:42:46,730
Director Pan called me today.

839
00:42:47,690 --> 00:42:48,650
Dad.

840
00:42:50,300 --> 00:42:51,170
Sorry!

841
00:42:51,780 --> 00:42:52,650
Don't need to say.

842
00:42:54,690 --> 00:42:56,130
It's mom and dad's fault.

843
00:42:58,020 --> 00:42:59,600
Yang. Sorry!

844
00:43:00,610 --> 00:43:02,020
Sorry to let you suffer.

845
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:04,260
