846
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:06,970
If you don't want to study science you can talk to us.

847
00:43:06,970 --> 00:43:09,260
Why did you go back to school secretly
 to change the division table?

848
00:43:11,260 --> 00:43:12,410
I was wrong.

849
00:43:13,060 --> 00:43:13,980
Yang.

850
00:43:14,170 --> 00:43:15,120
I admit that

851
00:43:15,780 --> 00:43:18,300
your mother and I were too arbitrary in this matter.

852
00:43:18,970 --> 00:43:20,370
We made the decision for you

853
00:43:20,370 --> 00:43:21,450
without asking your opinion.

854
00:43:23,130 --> 00:43:24,340
We apologize to you.

855
00:43:25,740 --> 00:43:26,930
I have discussed this with your mother.

856
00:43:27,650 --> 00:43:30,540
We will go to school to plead for you tomorrow.

857
00:43:31,540 --> 00:43:34,100
We have a great responsibility in this matter.

858
00:43:35,210 --> 00:43:36,820
If your director punishes you,

859
00:43:37,540 --> 00:43:38,540
I'll take care of it for you.

860
00:43:40,130 --> 00:43:41,260
I was wrong.

861
00:43:42,930 --> 00:43:45,890
No, you were not. Come.

862
00:43:46,780 --> 00:43:48,300
I won't force you anymore.

863
00:43:48,680 --> 00:43:49,780
Mom, sorry!

864
00:43:49,780 --> 00:43:51,890
I won't force you with a clipboard.

865
00:43:52,500 --> 00:43:53,820
It's good to be home.

866
00:43:54,260 --> 00:43:56,850
We thought you are running away from home.

867
00:44:11,060 --> 00:44:12,450
If you don't come back,

868
00:44:12,450 --> 00:44:13,740
we'll call the police.

869
00:44:14,340 --> 00:44:15,260
Mom, I was wrong.

870
00:44:16,500 --> 00:44:17,580
I won't do it again.

871
00:44:20,450 --> 00:44:20,980
Good.

